      <body>+1 This patch will make testing email rendering a lot easier in development and could replace the role of the [inaction_mailer gem](http://github.com/cwninja/inaction_mailer).

I've added some additional enhancements to the patch:

* Try to use the tmp directory in Rails Root and fallback to the system tmp directory
* Create the directory for the mail if it doesn't exist
* Write emails to users in the To, CC, and BCC field instead of just To

I've attached a test.</body>
      <body-html>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;+1 This patch will make testing email rendering a lot easier in
development and could replace the role of the &lt;a href=
&quot;http://github.com/cwninja/inaction_mailer&quot;&gt;inaction_mailer
gem&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I've added some additional enhancements to the patch:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Try to use the tmp directory in Rails Root and fallback to the
system tmp directory&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create the directory for the mail if it doesn't exist&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write emails to users in the To, CC, and BCC field instead of
just To&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I've attached a test.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
